{"tid":935784,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"一定係Band3廢青啦 家陣啲00後真係好垃圾【青年扮路障截車】","createTime":"2018-12-10T09:36:14.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-10T11:12:52.000Z","uid":225464,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"748a14fb8c8ee2975bf184eb6c6b6077bcc9ae86","tid":935784,"uid":225464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-10T09:36:14.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20181210/bkn-20181210171517925-1210_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20181210%2Fbkn-20181210171517925-1210_00822_001.html&d=qXvIiLPhcgzIZTgxll1D%2FghMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=2a1ab2b0\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20181210/bkn-20181210171517925-1210_00822_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\nLINK有片<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/999.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/e0m1yTV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fe0m1yTV.jpg&h=b30b05e0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>無聊當有趣？青年扮路障　搬雪糕筒攔途截車</strong><br />\n<br />\n警察不時會設置路障，被截停的司機可能都嚇一嚇。惟近日有青年疑因貪玩，搬動警方雪糕筒截停的士，惹來的士司機怒斥︰「玩嘢」！<br />\n<br />\n片段被上傳至Facebook群組「巴士的事討論區」，星期日（9日）凌晨四時許，一輛的士於尖沙咀加連威老道近科學館行駛時，有一名黑衣青年搬動印有警察字樣的雪糕筒，舉手截車。<br />\n<br />\n當時青年同行的幾名朋友分散在馬路兩旁，一人正舉機拍攝。當的士停下來後，黑衣青年上前詢問司機︰「去唔去紅磡？」司機反問是否上車時，該青年稱︰「我個朋友X你嘔，我拎開個垃圾桶畀你過先」。<br />\n<br />\n原來青年口中的「垃圾桶」即是警方雪糕筒，他將其搬至路旁後，與橙衣青年一起揮手，示意讓的士離開。他們的同行友人則不時爆出笑聲，似乎事情非常有趣。<br />\n<br />\n片段惹來網民的怒火，直斥︰「廢青」、「癡X線，即刻報警啦」、「咁大個人做埋啲無聊嘢」。<br />\n<br />\n事實上，胡亂放置雪糕筒隨時犯法！根據《道路交通條例》，任何人在未經運輸署署長、警務處處長或路政署署長同意下，移動、損壞或以任何方法干擾任何交通標誌或訂明的交通標誌，即屬犯罪。一經定罪，可被處罰款1,000港元及監禁3個月。"},{"pid":"2924b0650bd8cc73e413d9b71847c033b792bcc9","tid":935784,"uid":196924,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-10T09:36:49.000Z","msg":"叫佢冒警"},{"pid":"de6c0ad484f8ea316e6da049b81ec869652476f0","tid":935784,"uid":41245,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-10T09:37:31.000Z","msg":"抖音片<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"364c85f966b976943777f727296f9ae468306a87","tid":935784,"uid":71508,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-10T09:41:03.000Z","msg":"垃圾mk仔！😡😡"},{"pid":"84b73912413e79d31ab901930f2951bd644eeb5f","tid":935784,"uid":109983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-10T10:47:38.000Z","msg":"報警拉鳩佢啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62ccf52f11b4c69ea0a40ba09fa81645a4489939","tid":935784,"uid":146226,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-10T11:12:52.000Z","msg":"「我個朋友X你嘔，我拎開個垃圾桶畀你過先」唔喺好明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}